<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />

  <title>Taepyung Company Profile - 08</title>

  <style>
    @page {
      size: A4 landscape;
      margin: 0;
    }

    :root {
      --green: #387040;
      --light-green: #70C088;
      --cream: #F7F5EF;
      --black: #111111;
      --gray: #777777;
      --line: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.12);
    }

    * {
      box-sizing: border-box;
    }

    html,
    body {
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      font-family: Pretendard, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Noto Sans KR", sans-serif;
      background: #d9d9d9;
      color: var(--black);
      -webkit-print-color-adjust: exact;
      print-color-adjust: exact;
    }

    .page {
      position: relative;
      width: 297mm;
      height: 210mm;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 20mm 22mm 16mm;
      background: var(--cream);
      overflow: hidden;
    }

    /* Header */
    .topbar {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      align-items: flex-start;
      height: 14mm;
      margin-bottom: 18mm;
    }

    .logo-area {
      width: 42mm;
      height: 12mm;
      border: 1px dashed rgba(56, 112, 64, 0.35);
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      font-size: 8px;
      letter-spacing: 0.12em;
      color: var(--green);
      font-weight: 700;
    }

    .logo-area img {
      width: 100%;
      max-height: 100%;
      object-fit: contain;
      display: block;
    }

    .doc-label {
      padding-top: 1mm;
      font-size: 8px;
      line-height: 1.55;
      letter-spacing: 0.06em;
      color: var(--gray);
      text-align: right;
    }

    /* Main Layout */
    .layout {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 0.78fr 1.22fr;
      gap: 20mm;
      height: 128mm;
    }

    .left,
    .right {
      min-width: 0;
    }

    .left {
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      justify-content: space-between;
    }

    .eyebrow {
      font-size: 8.5px;
      line-height: 1;
      letter-spacing: 0.22em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: var(--green);
      font-weight: 800;
      margin-bottom: 9mm;
    }

    h1 {
      margin: 0;
      font-size: 30px;
      line-height: 1.16;
      letter-spacing: -0.065em;
      font-weight: 760;
    }

    .lead {
      margin-top: 12mm;
      max-width: 82mm;
      font-size: 13px;
      line-height: 1.85;
      letter-spacing: -0.035em;
      color: #222;
      word-break: keep-all;
    }

    .summary-box {
      width: 82mm;
      border-top: 1.5px solid var(--green);
      padding-top: 5.5mm;
    }

    .summary-title {
      font-size: 25px;
      line-height: 1;
      letter-spacing: -0.06em;
      color: var(--green);
      font-weight: 780;
      margin-bottom: 4mm;
    }

    .summary-text {
      max-width: 70mm;
      font-size: 10px;
      line-height: 1.7;
      letter-spacing: -0.025em;
      color: #444;
      word-break: keep-all;
    }

    /* Right Layout */
    .featured-area {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
      gap: 5mm;
      height: 48mm;
      margin-bottom: 5mm;
    }

    .featured-visual {
      position: relative;
      background: var(--green);
      overflow: hidden;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.78);
      font-size: 8px;
      letter-spacing: 0.16em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
    }

    .featured-visual img {
      width: 100%;
      height: 100%;
      object-fit: cover;
      display: block;
    }

    .featured-copy {
      padding: 6mm;
      background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.68);
      border: 1px solid var(--line);
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      justify-content: space-between;
    }

    .featured-label {
      font-size: 8px;
      line-height: 1;
      letter-spacing: 0.16em;
      color: var(--green);
      font-weight: 800;
      text-transform: uppercase;
    }

    .featured-title {
      margin: 0;
      font-size: 19px;
      line-height: 1.18;
      letter-spacing: -0.06em;
      color: #111;
      font-weight: 780;
      word-break: keep-all;
    }

    .featured-desc {
      margin: 0;
      font-size: 9.8px;
      line-height: 1.65;
      letter-spacing: -0.025em;
      color: #444;
      word-break: keep-all;
    }

    /* Product Groups */
    .group-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
      gap: 5mm;
      height: 75mm;
    }

    .group-card {
      padding: 6mm;
      background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.68);
      border: 1px solid var(--line);
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      justify-content: space-between;
      overflow: hidden;
    }

    .group-card.primary {
      background: var(--green);
      border-color: var(--green);
      color: #fff;
    }

    .group-index {
      font-size: 7.5px;
      line-height: 1;
      letter-spacing: 0.16em;
      color: var(--green);
      font-weight: 800;
      margin-bottom: 5mm;
    }

    .group-card.primary .group-index {
      color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.72);
    }

    .group-title {
      margin: 0 0 4mm;
      font-size: 15.5px;
      line-height: 1.22;
      letter-spacing: -0.055em;
      font-weight: 760;
      word-break: keep-all;
    }

    .group-desc {
      margin: 0;
      font-size: 9.4px;
      line-height: 1.65;
      letter-spacing: -0.025em;
      color: #444;
      word-break: keep-all;
    }

    .group-card.primary .group-desc {
      color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.78);
    }

    .product-list {
      margin: 5mm 0 0;
      padding: 0;
      list-style: none;
      border-top: 1px solid rgba(56, 112, 64, 0.18);
    }

    .group-card.primary .product-list {
      border-top-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.22);
    }

    .product-list li {
      padding: 2.6mm 0;
      border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(56, 112, 64, 0.12);
      font-size: 8.5px;
      line-height: 1.45;
      letter-spacing: -0.025em;
      color: #444;
      word-break: keep-all;
    }

    .group-card.primary .product-list li {
      color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.8);
      border-bottom-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.16);
    }

    .tag {
      margin-top: 4mm;
      font-size: 7.5px;
      line-height: 1;
      letter-spacing: 0.14em;
      color: rgba(56, 112, 64, 0.78);
      text-transform: uppercase;
      font-weight: 750;
    }

    .group-card.primary .tag {
      color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.72);
    }

    /* Footer */
    .footer {
      position: absolute;
      left: 22mm;
      right: 22mm;
      bottom: 9mm;
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      align-items: flex-end;
      font-size: 7.5px;
      line-height: 1.45;
      color: var(--gray);
    }

    .footer-logo {
      font-weight: 750;
      letter-spacing: -0.02em;
      color: var(--green);
    }

    .page-no {
      letter-spacing: 0.08em;
      color: rgba(56, 112, 64, 0.65);
    }

    @media print {
      html,
      body {
        width: 297mm;
        height: 210mm;
        background: #fff;
      }

      .page {
        margin: 0;
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>

<body>

  <section class="page">

    <header class="topbar">
      <div class="logo-area">
        LOGO
        <!-- 로고 넣을 때 -->
        <!-- <img src="assets/taepyung-logo-green.svg" alt="Taepyung"> -->
      </div>

      <div class="doc-label">
        Company Profile<br />
        Ver. 2025-V1
      </div>
    </header>

    <main class="layout">

      <section class="left">
        <div>
          <div class="eyebrow">New Products</div>

          <h1>
            브론디의 제품 경험을<br />
            확장하는 신제품과<br />
            대표 제품 라인업
          </h1>

          <p class="lead">
            브론디는 가정용 화장지부터 키친타올, 점보롤, 핸드타올까지
            다양한 사용 환경에 맞춘 제품 라인업을 지속적으로 확장하고 있습니다.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="summary-box">
          <div class="summary-title">Expanded</div>
          <div class="summary-text">
            향, 소재, 사용 방식, 대용량 수요까지 고려한 제품 확장을 통해
            일상과 업무 공간의 위생 경험을 넓혀갑니다.
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="right">

        <div class="featured-area">
          <div class="featured-visual">
            PRODUCT IMAGE
            <!-- <img src="assets/blondy-new-product.jpg" alt="브론디 신제품"> -->
          </div>

          <div class="featured-copy">
            <div class="featured-label">Featured Line</div>

            <h3 class="featured-title">
              생활 가까이에 놓이는<br />
              브론디 제품군
            </h3>

            <p class="featured-desc">
              부드러운 사용감, 위생적인 관리, 다양한 용도에 맞춘 제품 구성으로
              가정과 상업 공간 모두에서 사용할 수 있는 라인업을 제공합니다.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="group-grid">

          <div class="group-card primary">
            <div>
              <div class="group-index">01</div>
              <h3 class="group-title">화장지 라인</h3>
              <p class="group-desc">
                향과 소재를 달리한 30m 제품군으로 일상 사용감을 세분화합니다.
              </p>

              <ul class="product-list">
                <li>브론디 라벤더</li>
                <li>브론디 순수 소프트</li>
                <li>브론디 에코라벤더</li>
              </ul>
            </div>

            <div class="tag">Tissue Line</div>
          </div>

          <div class="group-card">
            <div>
              <div class="group-index">02</div>
              <h3 class="group-title">키친타올 라인</h3>
              <p class="group-desc">
                뽑아쓰는 타입과 롤타입 제품으로 주방 사용 환경에 대응합니다.
              </p>

              <ul class="product-list">
                <li>브론디 뽑아쓰는 키친타올</li>
                <li>브론디 데일리 키친타올</li>
                <li>브론디 플러스 키친타올</li>
              </ul>
            </div>

            <div class="tag">Kitchen Towel</div>
          </div>

          <div class="group-card">
            <div>
              <div class="group-index">03</div>
              <h3 class="group-title">비하프 라인</h3>
              <p class="group-desc">
                대용량 사용과 위생 관리가 필요한 공간을 위한 제품군입니다.
              </p>

              <ul class="product-list">
                <li>비하프 점보롤 300m</li>
                <li>비하프 점보롤 200m</li>
                <li>비하프 핸드타올</li>
              </ul>
            </div>

            <div class="tag">B-Half Line</div>
          </div>

        </div>

      </section>

    </main>

    <footer class="footer">
      <div class="footer-logo">TAE PYEONG PAPER</div>
      <div class="page-no">08</div>
    </footer>

  </section>

</body>
</html>
